(1, 'g', 'What kind of repairs do you offer?', 'We offer a wide range of repairs including screen replacements, battery replacements, water damage repairs, software upgrades, and more', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:15:28', '2024-11-21 11:15:28'),
(2, 'g', 'How long will my repair take?', 'The time it takes to complete a repair depends on the type of repair and the availability of parts. We strive to complete repairs as quickly as possible and typically provide an estimated time frame when you drop off your device.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:15:44', '2024-11-21 11:15:44'),
(3, 'g', 'Do I need an appointment to bring repair for my device?', 'No, you do not need an appointment to bring in your device for repair. You can simply drop it off at our service center during our business hours. However, if you prefer to schedule an appointment, you can do so through our website or by phone.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:16:03', '2024-11-21 11:16:03'),
(4, 'r', 'How do I know if my device needs to be repaired?', 'If your device is experiencing issues such as a cracked screen, not turning on, overheating, slow performance, or any other issues, it may need to be repaired.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:16:26', '2024-11-21 11:16:26'),
(5, 'r', 'How much does a repair cost?', 'The cost of a repair depends on the type of device and the extent of the damage. Please contact us for a quote.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:16:36', '2024-11-21 11:16:36'),
(6, 'r', 'Can you repair device of all major brands?', 'Yes, we can repair devices from various brands as long as they are repairable and we have the necessary parts available.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:16:47', '2024-11-21 11:16:47'),
(7, 'n', 'How does the Nationwide repair service work?', 'You can send your device to us through a courier service. Once we receive your device, we will assess the problem and provide you with a quote. If you agree to the quote, we will proceed with the repair and send the device back to you once it is fixed.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:16:57', '2024-11-21 11:16:57'),
(8, 'n', 'Is it safe to send my device through a courier service?', 'We recommend using a reliable courier service to send your device. Once we receive your device, we take full responsibility for its safety and security.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:17:07', '2024-11-21 11:17:07'),
(9, 'n', 'How long will it take Nationwide repair service?', 'The time it takes to repair your device depends on the type of repair needed and the availability of parts. We strive to complete repairs as quickly as possible and will provide you with an estimated time frame when you agree to the quote.', NULL, '2024-11-21 11:17:18', '2024-11-21 11:17:18');

